STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Kelvin VAUGHAN, a/k/a Kelvin Vaughn and Calvin Vaughn, Defendant-Respondent. C-1027 September Term 2017
079232 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 1, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001998-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
